The defendant Terry L Raddant was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Terry L Raddant is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Terry L Raddant was found guilty of Deliver Cocaine (>40g) [Modifiers: Repeater, PTAC, as a Party to a Crime], a class C felony, Wisconsin Statutes 961.41(1)(cm)4.

For more information, see Wisconsin Statute 111.335 and the Department of Workforce Development's publication, Arrest and Conviction Records under the Law.
